title: Days of our Lives S52E208 Friday, July 14, 2017
description:
Brady is jealous when he finds Eric and Nicole together.





Determined to uncover the truth, Abigail plants a listening device in Dario’s office.





Steve tells Kayla he thinks someone might be framing her and begins to investigate.





A vengeful Jade contemplates stirring up trouble one last time before leaving town
